---
<section data-test="hero" style="padding:5rem 1.5rem 4rem;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-bg) 0%,var(--color-surface) 100%);">
  <div style="max-width:48rem;margin:0 auto;">
    <div data-test="version-badge" style="display:inline-block;background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:9999px;padding:0.25rem 0.875rem;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      v7.7.0
    </div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,6vw,3.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 1.25rem;color:var(--color-text);">
      Spec-Driven AI Development
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 2rem;">
      RootSpec is a methodology that gives AI agents a stable, testable specification to implement from — turning natural language product intent into working, validated software.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/demos/greenfield/#how-it-works" style="background:var(--color-primary);color:white;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">See How It Works</a>
      <a href="/demos/greenfield/#try-it" style="background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);color:var(--color-text);padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:0.5rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Try the Spec Wizard</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
